  <bioghist id="aspace_54bc37e7349682343ebae4bb8a454ea3">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>The Veterinary College Registrar's Office is the repository for all academic records for DVM students. The office assists DVM students to understand and complete the requirements for graduation.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_f68355bf0b20f92f0883e047848cf337">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Records of the Registrar of the College of Veterinary Medicine, Cornell University.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_169a28e1d0df196c4df817fa1cfb01ec">
    <head>SERIES LIST</head>
<p><emph render="bold"> Series I. Curriculum </emph> Box 1 </p><p> A collection of reports and correspondence relating to the curriculum review which took place in the mid 1980s. Included are reports of the Task Force to Review the Curriculum and the Committee to Review Examinations and Educational Process. The material was originally housed in one binder.</p>  </arrangement>
